title: Lower City Park public input meeting scheduled Wednesday
text:
Published By: Iowa City Press - Today 
The City will host two open houses Wednesday in the Social Hall of the Robert A. Lee Recreation Center, at 220 S. Gilbert St., in Iowa City....
